short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Browse the contents of ClojureScript data, browse and restore historic atom states.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Gadget inspector is a devtools extension that adds a panel where you can browse any data in your running application that is passed through `gadget.inspector/inspect` - a function from the companion library - https://github.com/cjohansen/gadget-inspector.
